the required links are as follows : 
1-to fetch all the tasks use : get localhost:3900/api/tasks
2-to search for a task use : get localhost:3900/api/tasks?searchKey=(title or description)&searchValue=(value)
3- to add a task use : post localhost:3900/api/tasks
4- to update a task : put localhost:3900/api/tasks/(the id of the task)
5-to delete a task : delete localhost:3900/api/tasks/(the id of the task)
